    "description": "<p>AST Corporate Services is a Public Accountants and Chartered Accountants firm in Singapore. We have a team of Chartered Accountants providing a full range of accounting services, tax compliance, tax planning, corporate secretarial, and other financial advisory services. We understand each and every client is unique. Our aim is to provide value-added services to our client which is personal, friendly, and professional.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We provide a friendly working environment, competitive employment package, and career advancement. We are a firm believer in staff development and training. As we grow, you grow.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
